00:00:00.719 --> 00:00:04.500
 

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:07.470
the Carson Hobby Magnifier is a hands-free

00:00:07.470 --> 00:00:11.740
or a hand-held lighted magnifier that includes 3 interchangeable lenses

00:00:11.740 --> 00:00:15.289
to choose from. this product has several
functions.

00:00:15.289 --> 00:00:20.699
it can be used as a tabletop magnifier,
a hands-free magnifier,

00:00:20.699 --> 00:00:22.869
a handheld magnifier

00:00:22.869 --> 00:00:27.419
as well as a book light. this product is ideal for cross stitching,

00:00:27.419 --> 00:00:31.590
needlepoint, crocheting, craftwork

00:00:31.590 --> 00:00:34.460
reading and many other hobbies.

00:00:34.460 --> 00:00:38.380
the Hobby Magnifier includes 3 lenses- a 2 power,

00:00:38.380 --> 00:00:42.970
a 2.5 power and 4 power dual lens.

00:00:42.970 --> 00:00:48.100
the 2 power lens is great for cross
stitching and other craft work.

00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:51.560
the 2.5 power fresnel lens is lightweight

00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:55.910
and allows users to view a broader
surface area. it also has a 3 power

00:00:55.910 --> 00:00:57.300
spot lens for viewing

00:00:57.300 --> 00:00:58.750
fine details.

00:00:58.750 --> 00:01:01.900
this lens is ideal for reading books and
other activities.

00:01:01.900 --> 00:01:06.750
the 4 powered dual lens provides high
magnification with minimal distortion.

00:01:06.750 --> 00:01:10.250
this lens is ideal for craftwork, hobbies

00:01:10.250 --> 00:01:15.040
crocheting, removing splinters and viewing other fine details.

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:18.280
to change the lenses simply push the
clip on the back in,

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:23.670
and slide the magnifier out. the magnifier
can be adjusted to your desired viewing

00:01:23.670 --> 00:01:24.280
angle.

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:28.210
the Hobby Magnifier can be used either on a
tabletop

00:01:28.210 --> 00:01:32.180
with the included based or remove the base
for handheld

00:01:32.180 --> 00:01:37.229
for hands-free use. simply attach the
next strap to use the Hobby Magnifier

00:01:37.229 --> 00:01:38.060
hands-free.

00:01:38.060 --> 00:01:41.540
the top portion and the magnifier can be
removed

00:01:41.540 --> 00:01:44.870
and the Hobby Magnifier can be used as a
book light.

00:01:44.870 --> 00:01:48.790
the 2 LED lights are extremely bright,
long-lasting

00:01:48.790 --> 00:01:51.790
and consume less energy than regular
incandescent bulbs.

00:01:51.790 --> 00:01:55.979
the light can be adjusted to your desired
angle.

00:01:55.979 --> 00:01:59.890
the 2 LED lights are powered by 3 triple A
batteries.

00:01:59.890 --> 00:02:04.430
the Carson Hobby Magnifier is the ideal
hands-free magnifier

00:02:04.430 --> 00:02:07.009
that provides magnification and light for
any activity

